/notes/Lenethailef.title: Lenethailef
/notes/Lenethailef.content: **Lenethailef** is a [[notes/Qal languages|Qal language]] spoken in the southwestern coastal regions of [[notes/Continent E|Continent E]]. It emerged as a distinct language around 1100 BP.
